snippet.title: RAILCRAFT SHORT GAMEPLAY
snippet.description:
RailCraft is a train and tracks game and consist of two part. First part is a fun and challenging levels of puzzle and second is creative mode which you can make your dream rail way and watch trains on it. 

RailCraft made by Ensar Eray Akkaya with Benders group. Soon you can play on PC, Mac and Android.

https://twitter.com/BendersGroup
https://www.linkedin.com/in/ensar-eray-akkaya-25a032155
